content:
You need to perform a few additional steps to complete your installation.

Assign Custom Object Permissions for Data Mapper Bundles and Data Mapper Map Items
Activate Record Pages for the Unmanaged Package
Assign Permission Set Licenses for Insurance Industries Extension Objects
Required Permissions for the Partner Community User Profile
Automatic Vlocity State Transition Component Refresh
Field-Level Security Permission Set for Insurance Industries Extension Objects and Fields in Installations
Complete Post-Install Steps for Contract Lifecycle Management for Insurance
title: Post-Installation Tasks for Insurance
